title: Morning Joe 3/17/21
description: A man captured in Georgia on Tuesday night is suspected in three shootings at Atlanta-area massage parlors or spas that killed eight people, officials said. NBC News' Blayne Alexander reports.
author: news.podcasts@nbcuni.com (NBC News)
